      "level": "H2",
      "text": "employer must record the number of hours worked in each classification at the prescribed",
      "page": 52
    },
    {
      "level": "H2",
      "text": "hourly base rate.",
      "page": 52
    },
    {
      "level": "H2",
      "text": "OVERTIME:",
      "page": 52
    },
    {
      "level": "H2",
      "text": "week, whichever gives the employee the greater wages.  At least time and one-half the base",
      "page": 52
    },
    {
      "level": "H2",
      "text": "rate is required for all overtime.  A laborer, workman or mechanic and an employer may",
      "page": 52
    },
